Addressing the rising churn at Fit.ly Tech requires a deep dive into account details, customer support logs, and user activity to pin down exactly why subscribers are leaving. The first step involves cleaning and validating these fragmented datasets to ensure the insights are based on accurate data. From there, a strategic KPI will be defined to help leadership track retention more effectively. Ultimately, these findings will be turned into practical, high-impact recommendations to help the Marketing and Product teams stabilize the user base heading into next quarter.
